thread.title: Prep Softball: Helias start time announced
thread.title_full: Prep Softball: Helias start time announced

author: News Tribune
title: Prep Softball: Helias start time announced
text:
The Helias Lady Crusaders will take on Logan-Rogersville in the Class 3 quarterfinals at 1 p.m. Saturday at Duensing Field. 
Helias (19-9) and Logan-Rogersville (21-7) edged their sectional opponents by one run to reach this point. 
The Lady Crusders defeated Sullivan 5-4 and the Lady Wildcats beat Carl Junction 11-10. 
The winner will advance to the state semifinals to face Warrenton (25-2) or Incarnate Word (15-3-1). The semifinals re scheduled for 2 p.m. on Oct. 23. 
Admission into the MSHSAA-sanctioned quarterfinal is $6. No school passes or discounted rates will be accepted. ï»¿
